{"tid":2009398,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[請求法律巴絲]  Popo不當使用約束構成體位性窒息風險 有無得告","createTime":"2020-05-09T17:02:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T00:37:15.000Z","uid":214085,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f696d00713b95c36cc4f88568245002f30bc4055","tid":2009398,"uid":214085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T17:02:20.000Z","msg":"成日見popo拉手足個時長時間㩒底佢係地下, even坐住、搵野壓住個人, 其實會有體位性窒息風險, 簡單黎講姐係抖唔到氣, 事實上亦都見到有人因為咁對住鏡頭大叫佢抖唔到氣,但popo都係唔理<br />\n原理其實大約可以用中學Bio學嘅呼吸原理解釋, 因為壓住左而令胸腔擴張唔到/壓住縮細, 導致窒息, 嚴重當然係死<br />\n係美國其實有案例係告police不當使用武力/誤殺, &nbsp;不過好似多數都係肥人被人不當約束而死, 因為體型大d, 重d, 壓住個時更加難抖氣。<br />\n咁係香港又有無機會呢? 其實唔單係拉手足, 路過嘅良好市民見到popo咁拉人法, 如果見佢有抖唔到氣既危險又或者已經抖唔到氣, 係米有理由可以救人而構成合理辯護或者係告返popo?  <br />\n好似依單野咁: <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200509/4BGGQYMIZZXEYKYB2V7J2BAWQE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3aQXDIH1mk03Si7tAA7-ximhYnItYxi8M6okroApvk7OC82VncwYs41PM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200509%2F4BGGQYMIZZXEYKYB2V7J2BAWQE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3aQXDIH1mk03Si7tAA7-ximhYnItYxi8M6okroApvk7OC82VncwYs41PM&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpR5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=027c7171\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200509%2F4BGGQYMIZZXEYKYB2V7J2BAWQE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3aQXDIH1mk03Si7tAA7-ximhYnItYxi8M6okroApvk7OC82VncwYs41PM&h=16b608aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200509/4BGGQYMIZZXEYKYB2V7J2BAWQE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3aQXDIH1mk03Si7tAA7-ximhYnItYxi8M6okroApv